                     <interp inst="t18201028-131-person1270" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 30th of October I saw Lowe holding Richards. I took him from her, and found 2 s. in his hand - he said he gave the beads to Cradgington. I went to Cradgington's lodgings and found them - he was not at home. I took him opposite to the office.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>RICHARDS'S Defence. I never had them.</p>
